{"tid":1210967,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國催淚彈輸港許可問題","createTime":"2019-06-12T14:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T15:13:24.000Z","uid":223002,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ae2eccbf44683f67ceaa9c3a7e0373a1282576","tid":1210967,"uid":223002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:48:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20141119/s00001/1416333178083\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20141119%2Fs00001%2F1416333178083&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2yy8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=31acc309\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20141119%2Fs00001%2F1416333178083&h=1148d1fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20141119/s00001/1416333178083</a><br />\n2014年11月19日星期三 <br />\n上一篇<br />\n英不撤催淚彈輸港許可<br />\n【明報專訊】英國外交國務大臣施維爾書面回覆英國國會，表示不會撤銷相關公司將催淚彈出口香港的許可證。他說英國政府未能核實香港警方施放的催淚彈，部分由英國公司生產，並指香港警方未有<span style=\"color: red;\">違反使用催淚彈準則</span>。本港警察公共關係科說，會根據政府採購規定，因應行動需要購入合適裝備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20141002/00176_057.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20141002%2F00176_057.html&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2yy8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=d02f341a\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20141002/00176_057.html</a><br />\n2014年10月2日 (四)<br />\n四年向港警售貨值226萬<br />\n根據《衞報》報道，Chemring對港銷售催淚彈，獲英政府發出出口牌照，該公司指銷售「符合及受到英國政府的嚴格規管」，無法評論是次事件之後的對港銷售政策，但指很明顯有檢討的需要。英國一個名為「反對軍火交易運動（CAAT）」的非政府組織，指英國過去四年共發出六張許可證，向香港警方出口了價值十八萬英鎊（約二百廿六萬港元）的催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n香港警方公共關係科總警司許鎮德昨在記者會上回應稱，武器有嚴格採購程序，購入任何裝備都是為了配合警方的行動需要。另外，美國白宮請願網站本周日再有人發起題為「<span style=\"color: red;\">停止向香港警方出售任何武器 因這些武器被用來攻擊和平市民</span>」的請願，至昨傍晚約有九百人聯署，若能在本月廿八日有十萬人聯署，白宮將需要就此作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20141118/53139475\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20141118%2F53139475&d=P3WkhlyCj4fBe8yrVMQ2yy8TOYGSXSADKPC8%2B0d5FCk%3D&h=a144eda4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20141118%2F53139475&h=abdeb894\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20141118/53139475</a><br />\n2014年11月18日<br />\n【雨傘革命】英國政府： 未能確定港警射英製催淚彈<br />\n英國周一決定，不會禁止向香港出口催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n當局在9月28日香港警察向爭取民主的示威者施放87枚催淚彈後，檢討催淚彈出口政策。英國外交及聯邦事務部國務大臣施維爾（HugoSwire）周一向國會提交書面檢討報告，指目前發出的唯一出口牌照，並無觸犯武器出口控制法，亦不會被吊銷。<br />\n<br />\n放維爾表示，政府未能從影片確定香港警方所施放的一些催淚彈是由英國公司製造。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>五年前雨革撤消唔到 由今日起係咪應該撤消催淚彈輸港許可??</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf51ace50925c1fcb6dc825771bf56c1ce0efd5","tid":1210967,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:51:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0efcaecc1f736de890f2be2563ca043fca34f874","tid":1210967,"uid":237715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"跟住用大陸制有毒催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa37348b4b9a1855f18f59489758cc98e6b902d3","tid":1210967,"uid":223002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0efcaecc1f736de890f2be2563ca043fca34f874","tid":1210967,"uid":237715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"跟住用大陸制有毒催淚彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T15:13:24.000Z","msg":"至少唔係前宗主國入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}